00:36:25,470 --> 00:36:26,750
to you mundane people,

590
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,810
but after I give them my magical touch,

591
00:36:28,810 --> 00:36:30,010
they become quality items

592
00:36:30,010 --> 00:36:31,250
for detoxification.

593
00:36:35,950 --> 00:36:37,410
That's easy for you to say.

594
00:36:38,910 --> 00:36:40,110
That child is so weak.

595
00:36:40,510 --> 00:36:41,150
If she

596
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:42,270
eats this stuff

597
00:36:42,790 --> 00:36:43,870
and really vomits

598
00:36:43,870 --> 00:36:44,930
everything in her—

599
00:36:45,630 --> 00:36:46,870
Don't jinx her.

600
00:36:49,390 --> 00:36:50,030
Listen.

601
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,490
I can definitely cure her.

602
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:57,030
You...

603
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:33,440
How is the child?

604
00:37:34,950 --> 00:37:37,480
She's a bit better after taking the medicine.

605
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:42,830
By the way,

606
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:44,510
there's something

607
00:37:44,630 --> 00:37:45,990
that I find strange.

608
00:37:46,390 --> 00:37:47,710
Why are there no young people

609
00:37:47,710 --> 00:37:48,750
in this village?

610
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,550
I'm afraid

611
00:37:50,630 --> 00:37:51,950
they either died

612
00:37:52,790 --> 00:37:53,550
or ran away

613
00:37:54,310 --> 00:37:55,570
because of the Zornia.

614
00:38:31,350 --> 00:38:32,270
You're awake!

615
00:38:32,590 --> 00:38:33,430
Miss,

616
00:38:33,910 --> 00:38:35,590
did you save me?

617
00:38:35,750 --> 00:38:36,320
Yes.

618
00:38:37,470 --> 00:38:38,270
It's nothing.

619
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:40,510
Are you feeling better?

620
00:38:40,750 --> 00:38:41,470
Da.

621
00:38:42,470 --> 00:38:43,330
-Grandma.
-Da.

622
00:38:43,810 --> 00:38:44,900
You're awake.

623
00:38:47,270 --> 00:38:48,150
Grandma.

624
00:38:51,230 --> 00:38:53,640
Miss, thank you.

625
00:38:53,760 --> 00:38:54,590
It's my pleasure.

626
00:38:54,590 --> 00:38:55,190
Thank you.

627
00:39:06,510 --> 00:39:07,230
Granny,

628
00:39:09,230 --> 00:39:10,230
where's that guy?

629
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:12,500
He went to the Zornia field.

630
00:39:23,870 --> 00:39:24,470
Father,

631
00:39:25,050 --> 00:39:26,380
you devoted yourself to the country and the people,

632
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:27,990
[The former chief constable of the Inspection Office, Xi Zhaoming]

633
00:39:27,030 --> 00:39:28,360
but you ended up

634
00:39:28,390 --> 00:39:29,790
being criticized by all.

635
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:31,710
Why aren't you angry?

636
00:39:32,440 --> 00:39:33,040
Why?

637
00:39:34,830 --> 00:39:36,890
The country asked everyone to obey me

638
00:39:37,100 --> 00:39:38,450
because it believed

639
00:39:39,390 --> 00:39:40,940
that I had some strengths

640
00:39:42,020 --> 00:39:44,590
and could endure the humiliation and bear the heavy burden.

641
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:45,720
I don't understand.

642
00:39:46,990 --> 00:39:47,590
Son,

643
00:39:49,060 --> 00:39:50,920
you'll understand in the future.

644
00:39:56,030 --> 00:39:57,030
Yuda is awake.

645
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:02,440
Are you unhappy?

646
00:40:03,590 --> 00:40:04,990
We saved someone.

647
00:40:07,750 --> 00:40:09,480
What's there to be happy about?

648
00:40:09,950 --> 00:40:11,750
As long as there is still Zornia,

649
00:40:11,750 --> 00:40:12,750
this kind of thing

650
00:40:12,950 --> 00:40:14,210
will happen every day.

651
00:40:15,190 --> 00:40:16,390
Can you save them all?

652
00:40:16,910 --> 00:40:18,430
I'll save them one by one.

653
00:40:21,390 --> 00:40:22,030
Granny.

654
00:40:22,850 --> 00:40:23,970
Who forced you all

655
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,460
to grow the Zornia?

656
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:28,430
They wouldn't give their names.

657
00:40:28,990 --> 00:40:30,830
They dress mysteriously too.

658
00:40:31,350 --> 00:40:33,710
I really don't know.

659
00:40:33,980 --> 00:40:35,550
If we foreigners

660
00:40:35,890 --> 00:40:37,480
want to stay here,

661
00:40:38,190 --> 00:40:38,950
we

662
00:40:39,430 --> 00:40:41,700
can only obey them.

663
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:47,840
Lanna Village won't be at peace

664
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:49,900
unless the Zornia is not eliminated.

665
00:40:52,030 --> 00:40:53,590
Why don't we settle this once and for all

666
00:40:53,590 --> 00:40:54,430
and burn it?

667
00:41:01,480 --> 00:41:02,070
Hey!

668
00:41:18,620 --> 00:41:19,880
You're too impulsive.

669
00:41:20,390 --> 00:41:21,390
Stop pretending.

670
00:41:21,590 --> 00:41:23,120
I know you wanted to burn it.

671
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:24,270
I just did

672
00:41:24,270 --> 00:41:25,470
what you wanted to do.

673
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:26,880
You're welcome.

674
00:41:31,010 --> 00:41:32,490
You burned

675
00:41:32,560 --> 00:41:33,980
the Zornia field.

676
00:41:34,390 --> 00:41:35,390
Those people...

677
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:38,150
won't forgive us.

678
00:41:39,110 --> 00:41:39,830
Granny,

679
00:41:40,350 --> 00:41:42,700
the perpetrator should be held accountable.

680
00:41:42,700 --> 00:41:44,100
If they ask you anything,

681
00:41:44,360 --> 00:41:45,760
just tell them the truth.

682
00:41:46,990 --> 00:41:48,630
What truth?

683
00:41:49,030 --> 00:41:50,690
You want them to come after me?

684
00:41:52,070 --> 00:41:53,670
Don't worry. With me here,

685
00:41:54,030 --> 00:41:55,190
they won't hurt you.

686
00:41:56,390 --> 00:41:59,310
What should we do?

687
00:42:03,670 --> 00:42:04,350
Granny.

688
00:42:06,950 --> 00:42:07,910
I promise you

689
00:42:08,900 --> 00:42:10,130
no one will force you

690
00:42:10,590 --> 00:42:11,990
to plant Zornia anymore.

